          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生少礼请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。唤卑人进帐，有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻得刘备军中有一单福划策，先生可知单福何人也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相听禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "单福家住在颖州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "其中必有细根由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "单名徐庶有名头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "如今落在刘备手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "丞相兴兵要神留。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "字表元直徐门后"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "程昱比他差八九，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "丞相我怜才早设计谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "要想收他我也无计求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "字表元直徐门后"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人既与刘备相投，恐无外人能下手，真乃可惜了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既与玄徳为好友"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相有心要用此人，却也不难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卑人素闻徐庶极孝。只消丞相差人，将徐母赚至许昌，令其修书元直，谅无不"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来之理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好。后堂摆宴，与先生同饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "四曹将→程昱",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "程昱→曹操",
