    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四曹将",
        "家将",
        "徐母",
        "曹操",
        "程昱"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四曹将、曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "各路烟尘起四方。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "相府门前住车轮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相在上，小人叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐母可曾接到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在府外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命众将前去迎接。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四曹将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四曹将同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母、四曹将同上，四曹将同扯四门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与丞相无来往，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四曹将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相有大事相商。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众将带路朝前往，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四曹将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太夫人到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "迈步且把二堂上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四曹将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐母到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四曹将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相在上，老身万福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太夫人少礼。请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太夫人一路之上，多受风霜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承问。请问丞相，我儿徐庶往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在新野，太夫人修书将他招回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿在新野依佐何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在新野扶助刘备，如玉陷于泥花之中。太夫人将他召回，奏知天子必有封赠也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "太夫人修书将他召，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这事其中有蹊跷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我闻家将言道：我儿在朝，官居议郎之职。如今又命我修书召他，其中是何道"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐太夫人不允前来，故言在京为官，以安太夫人之心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来你等用的鬼计。丞相，你可知道刘备是何等人物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃涿县小辈，妄称皇叔。所谓外君子内小人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老夫暗把美言讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言来怒满腔，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹丞相此言差矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身久闻刘备乃中山靖王之后，屈身下士，恭己待人。义气传于四方，仁声闻"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘备本是英雄將，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "相府如同刑口样，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言来怒洋洋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "击死奸贼赴无常！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反了吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来与我上了绑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆恶妇，敢掌打老夫！武士推出斩去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母背下。程昱上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀下留人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将身且把二堂上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相因何将徐母斩首？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恶妇百般叫骂，故而她他斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩了徐母，恐大事不利。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相若将她斩首，她子徐庶在彼，闻听此事，必然尽心相助刘备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你之见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将她放回，派人侍奉，每日伺候。套她笔迹修书，差人送至新野。徐庶乃是大"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "欲借曹操帐中刀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操要杀，就该开刀。为何又将老身放回？真真岂有此理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是老夫不斩与你，程先生言到他与你子有八拜之交。斩了你，如斩他母一般，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程先生为何多事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与元直曾交好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先生只管将我保，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生将徐母小心伺候。掩门！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻曹操多奸诈，今日一见果不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯母随小侄来吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母、程昱同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
